26
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,199
Aku... Ye Feng.

27
00:02:58,159 --> 00:02:59,599
Kau pelajar sekolah ni ke?

28
00:02:59,599 --> 00:03:00,280
Ya.

29
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,360
