35
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:19,960
Mestilah kenal.

36
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:23,039
Fei Ni dari Bengkel 1, Kilang Kapas Jiangmian No. 1.

37
00:03:23,039 --> 00:03:25,319
Aku dari pasukan bola keranjang Kilang Kapas Jiangmian No. 1.

38
00:03:31,879 --> 00:03:32,879
Yang ini...

39
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,159
