40
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:39,479
Wira yang selamatkan orang masa hujan lebat.

41
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:42,159
Saudara Fang Muyang, apa khabar.

42
00:03:42,439 --> 00:03:43,240
Nama aku Ye Feng.

43
00:03:43,639 --> 00:03:45,639
Kapten pasukan bola keranjang Kilang Kapas Jiangmian No. 1.

44
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,000
Apa khabar.

45
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:49,639
Aku Fang Muyang.

46
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,719
Kau ni...

47
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:52,560
Badan kau ni

48
