99
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,160
Aku bukan kekasih dia.

100
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:52,560
Aku pun tak mampu tolong dia.

101
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,759
Itu kau sendiri yang cakap.

102
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,519
