147
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:24,799
Kau masih ingat?

148
00:09:26,039 --> 00:09:27,039
Dulu kau tinggal sini.

149
00:09:28,279 --> 00:09:30,120
Ada teringat apa-apa?

150
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:42,720
