155
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:03,000
Abang, semangat!

156
00:10:03,639 --> 00:10:05,159
Abang, semangat!

157
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:10,159
Abang, semangat!

158
00:10:13,639 --> 00:10:14,559
