162
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:27,440
Nanti jatuh, baru tahu sakit.

163
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,639
Cepat turun, turun!

164
00:10:28,639 --> 00:10:30,759
Nenek hari ini beli aiskrim.

165
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:34,639
Selamat hari jadi, cepat turun!

166
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,559
Hari ini beli aiskrim.

167
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,159
Haohao!

168
00:10:38,159 --> 00:10:39,440
