174
00:10:48,879 --> 00:10:50,039
Terima kasih, kawan.

175
00:10:50,039 --> 00:10:50,919
Terima kasih.

176
00:10:50,919 --> 00:10:51,320
Tak apa.

177
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:52,240
Jom, balik rumah.

178
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,200
Jom.

179
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,360
