237
00:14:58,639 --> 00:15:00,679
Aku pun dah lama bergelut dalam fikiran.

238
00:15:01,159 --> 00:15:02,639
Memang dah tak ada cara lain.

239
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:04,000
Tolonglah, demi

240
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:06,200
aku jaga awak berhari-hari ni,

241
00:15:06,799 --> 00:15:08,320
