00:41:16,119 --> 00:41:17,800
Tapi Doktor Liang beritahu saya,

761
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:20,119
dia pun tak tahu hal Fang Muyang dah pulih.

762
00:41:20,320 --> 00:41:21,360
Jadi saya pun lebih berjaga-jaga.

763
00:41:21,360 --> 00:41:23,800
Saya tanya jururawat yang jaga Fang Muyang,

764
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:25,400
dan pesakit di wad sekeliling.

765
00:41:25,760 --> 00:41:27,679
Hasilnya semua kata,

766
00:41:27,760 --> 00:41:30,400
Fang Muyang belum berniat keluar hospital.

767
00:41:33,440 --> 00:41:34,239
Feng Lin,

768
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:37,440
kau kena tahu,

769
00:41:37,440 --> 00:41:40,320
ini sama macam menuduh wira berbohong.

770
00:41:41,360 --> 00:41:42,239
Kena berhati-hati.

771
00:41:46,559 --> 00:41:47,840
Ada bukti?

772
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:48,800
Pengarah Xu.

773
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:50,159
Tuan paling faham saya.

774
00:41:50,159 --> 00:41:51,280
Kalau tanpa asas,

775
00:41:51,280 --> 00:41:52,760
saya takkan cakap sesuka hati.

776
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:55,079
Pengarah, tengok ini.

777
00:41:55,360 --> 00:41:57,119
Ini surat pengesahan diagnosis dari hospital.

778
00:41:57,840 --> 00:41:58,960
Sudah tentu.

779
00:41:58,960 --> 00:42:00,880
Saya sangat percaya pada peribadi Fang Muyang.

780
00:42:01,760 --> 00:42:02,760
Saya cuma takut

781
00:42:03,719 --> 00:42:05,159
dia dipergunakan orang lain.

782
00:42:27,840 --> 00:42:28,599
Pegawai Tu.

783
00:42:29,239 --> 00:42:32,280
Kau tahu Pengarah Xu panggil aku sebab apa?

784
00:42:32,519 --> 00:42:33,519
Aku pun tak tahu.

785
00:42:33,519 --> 00:42:34,760
Tunggu sekejap lagi.

786
00:42:49,320 --> 00:42:49,840
Selamat sejahtera, Pengarah Xu.

787
00:42:49,920 --> 00:42:50,280
Baik.

788
00:42:52,000 --> 00:42:53,280
Selamat sejahtera, Pengarah Xu.

789
00:43:01,880 --> 00:43:03,760
Pengarah Xu, tuan cari saya?

790
00:43:03,760 --> 00:43:04,599
Fei Ni.

791
00:43:04,960 --> 00:43:07,679
Saya harap kau beritahu saya dengan jujur,

792
00:43:07,920 --> 00:43:09,400
Kawan Fang Muyang,

793
00:43:09,920 --> 00:43:12,320
sebenarnya dah pulih sepenuhnya atau belum?

